thread.title: Angelo Pisano

author: Angelo Pisano
title: Angelo Pisano
text:
It is nice to be able to reach out via the cases system on Five9's support portal, but it is odd that I haven't ever received notification when my case ticket has been closed by their staff.
Otherwise, as a customer of this software, I am pleased by their extensive documentation of the usage of their products and the quarterly check in with our account manager is also a nice way to catch up.
